headline: Leading Sureties Announce the Launch of SuretyBind
summary: Four industry-leading surety companies – Chubb, The Hartford, Liberty Mutual and Travelers – today announced the formation of SuretyBind, LLC, a technology company that will feature a shared digital infrastructure to advance the surety industry.
